Make an offline install of Windows ADK

#Download the Windows ADK
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-hardware/get-started/adk-install

#Open a Command Prompt window as administrator.
#Change to the directory that stores the Adksetup.exe file.

#Run and specify where the offline install files will be downloaded to.
adksetup /layout

#Copy the downloaded files to a location that the offline computer can access.
#Run the command below to install.
adksetup /features OptionId.DeploymentTools OptionId.WindowsPreinstallationEnvironment
